eference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">May 12,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Norman+Rockwell+Museum&amp;rft.atitle=Reference+photo+for+Education+%2838918%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcollection.nrm.org%2Fsearch.do%3Fid%3D550386%26db%3Dobject%26view%3Dfull&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARussian+Schoolroom\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.newspapers.com/clip/19031262/rockwell_work_is_stolen_from_clayton/\">\"Rockwell Work Is Stolen From Clayton Shop\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/St._Louis_Post-Dispatch\" title=\"St. Louis Post-Dispatch\">St. Louis Post-Dispatch</a></i>. June 26, 1973. p.&#160;13<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">April 7,</span> 2018</span>  &#8211; via newspapers.com.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=St.+Louis+Post-Dispatch&amp;rft.atitle=Rockwell+Work+Is+Stolen+From+Clayton+Shop&amp;rft.pages=13&amp;rft.date=1973-06-26&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newspapers.com%2Fclip%2F19031262%2Frockwell_work_is_stolen_from_clayton%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARussian+Schoolroom\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.today.com/id/17430445#.WRU5AFKZOiI\">\"Stolen Rockwell found in Spielberg's collection\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Associated_Press\" title=\"Associated Press\">Associated Press</a>. March 3, 2007  &#8211; via <a href=\"/wiki/Today_(U.S._TV_program)\" title=\"Today (U.S. TV program)\"><i>Today</i></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Stolen+Rockwell+found+in+Spielberg%E2%80%99s+collection&amp;rft.date=2007-03-03&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.today.com%2Fid%2F17430445%23.WRU5AFKZOiI&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARussian+Schoolroom\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Boehm, Mike (October 6, 2009). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/culturemonster/2009/10/spielberg-and-the-rockwell-painting-that-got-away.html\">\"Steven Spielberg and the Norman Rockwell painting that got away\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Los_Angeles_Times\" title=\"Los Angeles Times\">Los Angeles Times</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2010-02-17</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Los+Angeles+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Steven+Spielberg+and+the+Norman+Rockwell+painting+that+got+away&amp;rft.date=2009-10-06&amp;rft.aulast=Boehm&amp;rft.aufirst=Mike&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flatimesblogs.latimes.com%2Fculturemonster%2F2009%2F10%2Fspielberg-and-the-rockwell-painting-that-got-away.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARussian+Schoolroom\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Salit, Richard (April 18, 2010). <a rel=\"